brewery.brewery_description:
Volfas Engelman is an alcoholic beverages manufacturer in Kaunas, Lithuania.

The establishment of brewery „Volfas Engelman“ dates back to the 19th century. Today the brewery produces beer, cider, alcoholic mixed drinks, kvass and energy drinks. Volfas Engelman brewery is named after its two founders. Since 2012 the CEO of the company is Marius Horbačauskas. The number of employees is more than 230 - it makes Volfas Engelman the second largest brewery in Lithuania. At the moment 99,57 % of „Volfas Engelman“ shares belong to the Finnish „Olvi“ Company Group. “Olvi” was established in 1878 by the brewer Williams Gideon Åberg and his wife Onni. At present it is the third largest producer of beer, cider and soft drinks in Finland.

beer.beer_description:
Tarpukario legenda Volfas Engelman su RINKTINIU alumi į šiandien sugrįžo ir vėl kaip anuomet aktuali patapo. Tarpukario Kauno didžiausias bravoras šiuo vardu vadinamas buvo ir populiariausią anuomet Lietuvoje alų virė. Šviežias tada ir todėl šviežias dabar Volfas Engelman RINKTINIS tik iš tyro, specialaus paruošimo vandens kuriamas, prabangą jojo aromatiniai Perle ir Magnum apyniai bei išskirtinės alaus mielės atskleidžia, o lietuviškas Pilzeno tipo salyklas jį šviesia spalva apdovanoja. RINKTINIS – yra bravoro vėliavnešys, jis kaip ir kitos Volfas Engelman rūšys pilamas į pintos talpos butelius, NEPASTERIZUOTAS todėl ir namuose galima jį ragauti tokį pat kaip ir bare.

The interwar legend Volfas Engelman returned to today with RINKTINIS beer and became as relevant as it had been before. The interwar Kaunas greatest brewery was named by the name and cooked the most popular beer in Lithuania at that time. Fresh then and due to that fresh now Volfas Engelman RINKTINIS is created only from fresh specially prepared water, its luxury is revealed by luscious Perle and Magnum hops and exclusive beer yeast and the Lithuanian Pilsen type malt presents it with light colour. RINKTINIS is the banner-bearer of the brewery, it as other Volfas Engelman sorts is bottled in bottles of pint volume, NON-SCALDED, so its taste is the same at home as in the bar.

Pasaulio skoniai: INDIA PALE ALE
Pilsner and carared malts
Equinox, Chinook, Cascade and Magnum hops

Australian Pale Ale. Hops: Ella (AUS), Galaxy (AUS), Rakau (NZ), Taurus (DE), Perle (DE)

Aksominio tamsumo, lengvas, todėl ypač tinkamas vasaros vakarams „BOHEMIJOS Tamsusis“ alus papildė Volfas Engelman šeimą. Karamelizuotas salyklas suteikia šiam alui prabangią raudonmedžio spalvą, lengvas ir malonus jo salstelėjęs skonis. Šis alus yra priskiriamas tamsaus Bohemian tipo alaus kategorijai. Skanaus ragavimo!

Velvety dark, soft due to that especially suitable for summer evenings “BOHEMIJOS Tamsusis” beer has complemented the Volfas Engelman family. Caramelized malt gives to this beer a luxurious mahogany colour, its sweetish taste is soft and pleasant. This beer is attributed to the category of dark beer of Bohemian type. Have a tasty gustation!

Our NEIPA is in no way inferior in its taste and aroma to the most famous and well-known NEIPA beers in the world. It is super fresh, fruity and quenches thirst with an exclusive aroma of citrus, tropical fruits, pineapple, lychee, melon and apricot.

11,6° PLATO, 8 EBC
Unlike many traditional lager type beers, Hoppy Lager is much more expressive, more intense dark amber–chestnut color, it has unique aroma of American hops, and a full, memorable flavor.

Volfas Engelman Bravoro pinta – pirmoji Lietuvoje pinta stiklo butelyje. Ne tik savo ūgiu ir formų elegantiškumu ji išskirtinė esti. Unikali šio alaus ketverto rūšių apynių kompozicija: išauginti Vokietijos ir Čekijos žemėse tauraus aromato Saaz, aromatiniai Hallertauer Mittelfrüh, kartieji Hallertauer Magnum ir Hallertauer Taurus. Dėl jų šis alus toks ypatus, kad net didžiausialaus žinovai jam kepures kelia. Dar vienas išskirtinumas, kad pirkdami šį alų, kaip ir kitas Volfas Engelman rūšis, visada galite matyti ir rinktis jį šviežią, nes etiketėje žymima ne tik galiojimo, bet ir pagaminimo data. Dabar ir pintos talpos skardinėje.

Volfas Engelman Brewery Pint is the first pint in Lithuania in a glass bottle. It is exclusive not only by its height and elegancy of forms. The composition of this beer four sorts hops is unique: grown in Germany’s and Czechia’s lands Saaz of noble aroma, the aromatic Hallertauer Mittelfrüh, the bitter Hallertauer Magnum and Hallertauer Taurus. Due to it this beer is so special that the biggest connoisseurs of beer raise hats to it. There is one more exclusive fact: when purchasing this beer just as the other sorts of Volfas Engelman you can always see and choose it fresh, as in the label both the production and the best before dates are indicated. Now in a tin of pint volume as well.

1410 „Šviesusis“ is a malt pale lager produced of water, roasted and light malt barley and hops. The beer is of transparent golden colour, it decorates the cup with thick foam of dazzling whiteness. Loved by everybody due to balanced taste intensity and lightness which is invigorated by slightly felt hops bitterness.

BORDO beer is made according to the recipe of our brew-masters, using a special mixture of light and roasted barley malt, water of special preparation, adapted to the type of hops.
Caramelized malt gives this beer a rich burgundy color. This beer has a slightly sweet taste that makes it so richly full, yet gentle and easy to drink.
